{"tid":2488000,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"浙江義烏市話你聽 走資會凍結你戶口","createTime":"2021-04-14T02:53:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T02:53:33.000Z","uid":48081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e1625ff4dc56cd0971abaa6b54af652df749a280","tid":2488000,"uid":48081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T02:53:33.000Z","msg":"怪事年年有，近年特別多。浙江義烏市公安局日前發表〈致全國各地公安機關的一封信〉（下簡稱〈一封信〉），呼籲各地公安不要對當地銀行賬戶「選擇性執法」。<span class=\"red\">事緣中央政府嚴打外滙流失，身為外貿重鎮的義烏首當其衝，被視為「假貿易」走資黑洞，因此各地公安做足120%，每見有銀行戶口跟義烏來往便動輒凍結，令當地商戶叫苦連天。</span>今次由地方公安向「全國」提出異議，非常罕見，或反映義烏經濟陷入絕境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E9%BB%9E%E8%A9%95-%E7%BE%A9%E7%83%8F%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89vs%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89-195300176.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E7%2583%258F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589vs%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589-195300176.html&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzvnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=735bd53e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E9%BB%9E%E8%A9%95-%E7%BE%A9%E7%83%8F%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89vs%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89-195300176.html</a>"}]}